<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n09002c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n09" href="#n09002c">N09 (VI.B.1)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n09all.htm#n09002c"> 2(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> object of the presence / (coffin)</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><b>Mental Hospital / Coffin Placed Inside Asylum Grounds / &ldquo;A Disgraceful Act.&rdquo;</b> &hellip; At the meeting of the Committee of Management of the Ballinasloe Mental Hospital on Monday last, an occurrence of a rather sensational character took place. / As the members filed in the main gate to go to the committee rooms, they were astonished to find that during the night or early hours of the morning a coffin had been placed inside the main gates, adjacent to the head attendant&apos;s house. The <mark>coffin</mark> belonged to the institution and was apparently taken from the stores during the night or early morning and placed there. The members stopped to gaze on the coffin, and notwithstanding exhaustive inquiries as to how it came there, failed to ascertain the <mark>object of its presence</mark>. <small> <a name="CT16feb24" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#CT16feb24"><cite title="source">Connacht Tribune</cite></a> (16 February 1924) 6/1</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
